      </div>
      <div class="reveal-right">
        <div class="glass-card card-featured rounded-2xl p-8 sm:p-10">
          <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-3">See It in Action</h2>
          <p class="text-primary-300 mb-8">
            Reach out and our team will show you how AI-powered visibility optimization can grow your brand.
          </p>
          <div class="space-y-6">
            <div class="p-5 bg-primary-900/50 rounded-xl border border-primary-700/50">
              <h3 class="font-heading text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-2">What to Expect</h3>
              <ul class="text-primary-300 text-sm space-y-2">
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
