                  AI visibility audit of your brand
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                  <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-accent-400 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
                  Competitive landscape analysis
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                  <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-accent-400 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
                  Custom GEO strategy recommendations
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                  <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-accent-400 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
